                <h1>Discover the Vibrant World of Henri Matisse</h1>
                <p>Henri Matisse was a leading figure in modern art, renowned for his use of vibrant colors and innovative techniques. His work spanned various styles, including Fauvism, where he emphasized bold color over realism. Matisse's legacy continues to influence artists worldwide, making him a pivotal player in the evolution of 20th-century art.</p>
